Package: clawboot
Version: 1.0.1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Imran Duratbegovic <imranduratbegovicc@gmail.com>
Depends: sudo, systemd, libc6, libstdc++6, libgcc-s1
Description: Graphical OpenClaw setup for Raspberry Pi 5
 ClawBoot installs OpenClaw, a local Gemma 4 E2B model, and optional
 Telegram or WhatsApp messaging through a simple desktop wizard.
 The package bundles its application and browser-facing runtime and does not
 require optional GTK, WebKit, Python, or development packages.
